{"tid":1678913,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"修例風波：理大博士畢業禮　校長拒與戴口罩學生握手","createTime":"2019-10-28T01:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T02:48:35.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9bc4bcf6481d1b26fc8a5516a2f329df186308","tid":1678913,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191027/photo/bkn-20191027131029599-1027_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191027133104\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191027%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191027131029599-1027_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191027133104&h=00cffce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學今(27日)舉行博士畢業禮，校長滕錦光在畢業禮致詞時表示，當前社會產生嚴重分歧，令人擔憂，懇請各方加強溝通，使暴力在香港消失，讓社會盡快走出困局，回復原來的秩序。<br />\n滕又指，希望能秉持大學教育的理念，以尊重和理性的態度表達意見，擁抱多元文化，容納不同觀點。在履行自己的職責之餘，亦要尊重他人的權利。<br />\n在畢業典禮頒授儀式期間，先後有2名畢業生戴口罩上台，而滕則沒有與他們握手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191027/photo/bkn-20191027131029599-1027_00822_001_02p.jpg?20191027133104\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191027%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191027131029599-1027_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20191027133104&h=58d155c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e399d7b7d317900c167e5034b91ecc94c1e5d21","tid":1678913,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"8a2eb9f462c8a61871f35b37235a862d26b9cec7","tid":1678913,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:54:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今年畢業嘅<br />\n<br />\n全部戴口罩上台<br />\n</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff193f26649071f54d32f97c143b795819ca55fd","tid":1678913,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"到底係邊一邊拒絕都未知zz 貪佢隻手有金?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794f92298df485f9b51026838975a61ac2dc35a7","tid":1678913,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"垃圾校長"},{"pid":"d0b84594b116e35b2a710821e202e414c8a12d0b","tid":1678913,"uid":291167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T02:48:35.000Z","msg":"理工人嘅恥辱"}]}